These rules are to be followed when making a PR in the master branch

- Remove unnessary comments from main.css, manifest.css, fonts.css, minify bootstrap.min.css, font-awesome.css, owl.carsousel.min.css, owl.theme.green.min.css.
- Minify main.css, manifest.css, fonts.css, bootstrap.min.css, font-awesome.css, owl.carsousel.min.css, owl.theme.green.min.css.
- Remove unnessary comments from manifest.js, functions.js, swHelper.js, jquery-3.2.1.min.js, owl.carousel.min.js, scrollreveal.min.js, sw.js.
- Minify manifest.js, functions.js, swHelper.js, jquery-3.2.1.min.js, Materialize.js, owl.carousel.min.js, scrollreveal.min.js, sw.js.
- Minify manifest.json.
- Remove comments from manifest.html & index.html (Note: online tools don't remove comments from scripts inside .html files sometimes).
- Remove all importing stylesheet lines from page.
- Make bootstrap.min.css, owl.carousel.min.css and owl.theme.green.min.css as internal style.
- Serve materialize.css from "https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/materialize/0.100.2/css/materialize.min.css".
- Make main.css, fonts.css and manifest.css as internal styles. (Note: Remember to change the path for images in the css styles)
- Serve materilize.js as "https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/materialize/0.100.2/js/materialize.min.js".
- Merge swHelper.js and Manifest.js into one file. remove swHelper.js call from manifest.html
- Minify the final manifest.html and index.html files.
- Run and Check if everything is functional. (Make Issue if any error occur)
- Make sure the pull request on master contains [V{{Version.Number}}.{{Version.MajorUpdate.Number}}.{{Version.MinorUpdate/BugFix.Number}}] {{Pull Request Title}}.
- Delete external files.
